      "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "OpenClaw writes JSONL to `~/.openclaw/metrics.jsonl` (Alloy tails → Loki). Paperclip stats come from its PostgreSQL database. The header stat row is a **Wave 2 placeholder** — full tokens/latency metrics arrive when OpenClaw + Open WebUI push to **InfluxDB**. Wing telemetry (`callback_plugins/glasswing_telemetry.py`) streams agent runs to Loki today."
      }
    },
    {
